'''International Animation Cartoon Festival Bangladesh (IACFB)''' is an annual international Animation film festival in Bangladesh for animated films. The first edition of the festival took place on 29 March 2013 at the Shishu Academy in Dhaka. Children Communication Bangladesh (CCB) has been organizing this festival based on the theme ''Shishura Shajabey Notun Prithibi'' the animation festival 1st time planing Md.Rabiul Islam Rony, Director of CCB.<ref>{{cite news|title=3-day animation fest features local, foreign cartoons|url=http://www.newagebd.com/detail.php?date=2013-03-31&nid=44547|accessdate=26 April 2014|newspaper=New Age|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426234944/http://www.newagebd.com/detail.php?date=2013-03-31&nid=44547|archivedate=26 April 2014|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=2nd Int'l Animation Cartoon fest ends today|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/entertainment/2nd-intl-animation-cartoon-fest-ends-today-21140|accessdate=26 April 2014|newspaper=The Daily Star}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Intâ€™l cartoon fest wraps up in style|url=http://www.daily-sun.com/index.php?view=details&archiev=yes&arch_date=25-04-2014&type=Int%C3%A2%E2%82%AC%E2%84%A2l-cartoon-fest-wraps-up-in-style&pub_no=835&cat_id=1&menu_id=7&news_type_id=1&index=1 |newspaper=Daily Sun |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427010625/http://www.daily-sun.com/index.php?view=details&archiev=yes&arch_date=25-04-2014&type=Int%C3%A2%E2%82%AC%E2%84%A2l-cartoon-fest-wraps-up-in-style&pub_no=835&cat_id=1&menu_id=7&news_type_id=1&index=1 |archive-date=27 April 2014 |access-date=26 April 2014}}</ref>

